lead_paragraph: The Euroleague's most successful coach Zeljko Obradovic will be aiming to add a ninth trophy to his collection when he takes Turkish giants Fenerbahce Istanbul to the Final Four of basketball's premier club competition next weekend.

headline.print_headline: Fenerbahce's Obradovic Seeking a Record Ninth Title
